text: Winchmore is a farming settlement in the Ashburton District, New Zealand. It is situated 12 kilometers west of Ashburton and 22 kilometers southeast of Methven on State Highway 77. It had a primary school that closed in 1927, has a community hall and research weather station. ==Climate== == References == Category:Settlements in Canterbury Region Category:Ashburton District
